   11.(x) RAISING CAIN, by Dan Kindlon and Michael Thompson
</P>
<P>
   with Teresa Barker. (Living Planet/Ballantine, $14.)
</P>
<P>
   The emotional life of boys.
</P>
<P>
   12.(x) THE LEXUS AND THE OLIVE TREE, by Thomas L.
</P>
<P>
   Friedman. (Anchor, $15.) A journalist explains the
</P>
<P>
   instant electronic global economy.
</P>
<P>
   13.(x) THE PROFESSOR AND THE MADMAN, by Simon Winchester.
</P>
<P>
   (HarperPerennial, $13.) How a murderer helped James
</P>
<P>
   Murray compile the Oxford English Dictionary.
</P>
