<HEADLINE>
NOTHING SUCCEEDS LIKE CONTROLLING SUCCESSION 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 By GUSTAV NIEBUHR   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Last week, Roman Catholics in New York began to take the measure
of their next archbishop, Edward M. Egan, who has been bishop of
Bridgeport, Conn., for more than a decade. At a press conference
