<P>
   ATLANTA _
</P>
<P>
   This Saturday night you can meet men, women and children who
have devoted themselves to protecting our environment. Check out
the hourlong special ``Heroes for the Planet'' at 7 p.m. on A&AMP;E.
The program pays tribute to people who help local and global
environmental causes. The show will be hosted by Haley Joel Osment,
