trips with pals. This story started more than a year ago, when a
friend of mine named Darrell bought an expensive 4-wheel-drive
pick-up truck. It ended last week in what has become known as ``The
Robby Saga,'' with a chain of events on a camp-out that provide a
testimonial to anyone that you best always listen to mama _ or
disaster can strike. By TOM STIENSTRA.
</P>
