being. As he stood in front of a small group of Manhattan city hall
reporters, searching and stumbling his way into a long overdue
admission about his ruined marriage, Giuliani faced the world with
a raw, heavy-hearted vulnerability that becomes an arrogant man. By
STEPHANIE SALTER.
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-TRADE (San Francisco) _ Congress should vote in favor of
fair trade and vote no on ``permanent normal trade relations.''
Perhaps it will help China to act in accordance with its ancient
values. And maybe it will be good for us not to kowtow to a big
bully. By DAVID SCHNEIDER.
</P>
