<DOCNO> NYT20000515.0113 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-15 13:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5450 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-GLOBAL-STOCK-MARKETS-     05-15 1047
