<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GLOBAL-STOCK-MARKETS-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
IN NEW ERA, STOCK MARKETS MUST FOCUS ON GLOBAL REACH 
</HEADLINE>
   (Commentary)  
 &HT;    
 &HT;    (To purchase this ``separate buy'' article from the New York
Times Syndicate please contact syndicate sales representative DEBRA
WEYDERT at 732-390-4480)
 &HT;    
 &HT;    
 By DAN COLARUSSO  
 c.2000 TheStreet.com  
<TEXT>
