<DOCNO> NYT20000515.0128 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-05-15 14:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5505 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e BC-TV-FALL-BOS &LR;      05-15 1228
