<P>
   IF YOU GO &QL; 
GETTING THERE: &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
Catalina Express runs to Catalina several times a day from San
Pedro, Long Beach and Dana Point. On Saturday from San Pedro, for
example, the boats run at 7:15 a.m., 9 a.m., 10:45 a.m., 1 p.m.,
2:45 p.m., 5 p.m. and 6:15 p.m. Round-trip fare is $38 for adults,
$28.50 for children (age 2 to 11), $34.50 for seniors (age 55 and
up). Information and reservations: (310) 519-1212. Web:
www.CatalinaExpress.com. Catalina Cruises also serves Long Beach.
Phone: (800) 228-2546. Web: www.catalinacruises.com.
</P>
