1900s are rare, and this particular performance by Cliburn three
years ago in San Antonio ranks as one of the more memorable moments
in Tim Madigan's life. Madigan reflects on that night in San
Antonio, and relates the impressions of a trumpet player in the San
Antonio symphony that accompanied Cliburn that night, and of Tim's
